Challenge Tier 4

Offer to the Undercity's Spirit Brazier in Kurast to alter its rewards:
{icon:bullet,1.2} Completing the dungeon with at least Attunement Rank 1 reward several Uniques, with an increased chance of a Mythic Unique.
Very rarely found from defeating Summoned Bosses, as well as randomly in Sanctuary.
